{"title":"平凡的赞歌","authors":["丁芒"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡的赞歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布彩霞的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——油漆工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞是最美的了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼就消失；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有你布下的彩霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久久地不褪色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的彩霞是什么做成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么鲜丽，这么浓烈？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻黄、钢红、山青、水碧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加上如火的气息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代最美的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你都去采集，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酿成最美的云霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贮满你的色碟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，在你的漆笔下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处有雷声，有火光，有奔腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的马蹄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了我们祖国的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五彩斑斓的足迹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春色最浓处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——养蜂人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘的是赶香车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走的是寻芳路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里春色最浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在那里住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放出了蜜蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象撒出了网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从五彩的云霞里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"网来芳甜的露。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜂在箱里酿蜜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在心中画图："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样迈大步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把春光留得更多？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宿的是青草铺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃的是风霜露，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦了你一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜了千万户！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金砖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——书店营业员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从矿石，从流沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万次精选、淘洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才取得闪闪发光的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纯金的字句。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一本书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该是几万颗金砂炼铸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熔化它的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是智慧与希望的火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，这一迭迭金砖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等着你的调遣发落；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请让每一双伸向你的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有最大的满足！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你递给了书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也递去了一个嘱咐："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——就用结实的金砖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砌成“四化”的基础！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}